Download:

  nodejs.org
  inside the folder
    node -v  (package.json)
    npm init (Entry point index.js/testtut.js)
    Open the package.json file 
      enter "private" : true under version
    
  Install express
    npm install --save express
    npm install --save express-handlebars
    
  Open the file (index.js/testtut.js)
    Require express
    Set the port (app.set)
    Define routes
      / - most basic URL 
    res.send 
      Displays the msg in the browser page
    app.listen - to mention where the web application has to listen for the instructions
    console.log - to print statments to the log
    app.get - path,function
      req - HTTP request
      
    app.use - middlware
      
      
    
